{"website": "https://corporate.aldi.us/en/newsroom/aldi-covid-19-updates/a-message-to-our-customers/", "retailer": "aldi", "text": ["aldi covid-19 updates", "aldi covid-19 updates", "a message to our customers about coronavirus from our ceo, jason hart", "our teams are working diligently to keep our shelves stocked and we are continuing to react to the covid-19 situation. in the midst of increased demand and challenging supply, we are focused on the products you are likely to want most: water, pantry staples, pre-made meals, cleaning supplies, toilet paper and more. to support as many customers as possible, you may see quantity limits placed on select items. we appreciate your patience as some of these products may be temporarily unavailable in some of our stores.", "if you have any additional questions regarding our response to covid-19, please use one of the following links:\u00a0", "previous aldi covid-19 updates"]}
