{"website": "https://www.frysfood.com/i/coronavirus-update/pharmacy", "retailer": "frys", "text": ["fry\u2019s food stores - pharmacy hours & online services-coronavirus update", "in response to the ongoing covid-19 pandemic, the kroger family of pharmacies will waive prescription delivery fees for both mail and courier, through january 31st, 2021. in many areas, if your order is placed by 11:00 a.m. local time, it can be processed the same day, and if it\u2019s after 11:00 a.m. local time, it will be processed the following business day. to learn more about the options and availability at your local pharmacy location, please contact your pharmacy directly.", "to protect the safety of our patients, associates and shoppers, the little clinic is is here for you and all your health need s 7 days a week. we offer services from cold & flu symptoms relief to covid-19 testing, rapid antibody testing and flu shots pls more. visit or schedule your appointment at ", "is covid-19 testing available at your pharmacies?", "no. testing is currently not available at our pharmacy locations. our clinics in select stores do offer covid -19 testing.", "is covid-19 testing available at your clinics?", "do your pharmacies or clinics offer  covid-19 antibody testing?", "yes. all pharmacies and clinics offer rapid antibody testing right in out stores. if you think you\u2019ve had covid 19, testing is just $25-dollars and typically provides results within 15 minutes for peace of mind. ", "what are the symptoms of covid-19?", "for the latest information on covid-19 symptoms and what you can do to better protect yourself, please refer to the "]}
