{"website": "https://www.frysfood.com/i/coronavirus-update/associate-wellness", "retailer": "frys", "text": ["fry\u2019s food stores - associate wellness - coronavirus update", "we\u2019re offering free covid-19 testing to associates based on symptoms and medical need. the kroger health testing solutions allows our associates feel more empowered and knowledgeable about their health, creating safer stores and facilities.", "we are continuing to enact our emergency leave guidelines, allowing paid time off for associates diagnosed with covid-19, placed under mandatory quarantine by their medical provider because of covid-19 or practicing self-isolation for symptoms verified by an accredited health care professional. all eligible associates will receive their standard pay for up to two weeks (14 days).", "for those affected by covid-19, kroger has also made $15 million available through the kroger family of companies "]}
