{"website": "https://www.walgreensbootsalliance.com/zh-hans/node/3801", "retailer": "walgreens", "text": [" how covid-19 changed pharmacy ", "the most popular item healthtex supplies walgreens is dr. sana camphor cubes for respiratory congestion, followed by dr. sana sodium bicarbonate powder \u2013 a heartburn remedy. but recently, something else cracked the top spots in florida, with appeal well beyond the latino communities. shortly after the coronavirus pandemic began, retailers were hit by a thermometer shortage. enter healthtex, which already was cleared by the fda to import medical devices and had a contact in china that manufactured high-quality thermometers."]}
