{"website": "https://www.fredmeyer.com/i/coronavirus-update/associate-wellness", "retailer": "fredmeyer", "text": ["fred meyer - associate wellness - coronavirus update", "we\u2019re offering free covid-19 testing to associates based on symptoms and medical need. the kroger health testing solutions allows our associates feel more empowered and knowledgeable about their health, creating safer stores and facilities.", "we are continuing to enact our emergency leave guidelines, allowing paid time off for associates diagnosed with covid-19, placed under mandatory quarantine by their medical provider because of covid-19 or practicing self-isolation for symptoms verified by an accredited health care professional. all eligible associates will receive their standard pay for up to two weeks (14 days).", "for those affected by covid-19, kroger has also made $15 million available through the kroger family of companies "]}
{"website": "https://www.fredmeyer.com/i/coronavirus-update/store-safety", "retailer": "fredmeyer", "text": ["fred meyer - store safety measures & information - coronavirus update", "as an employer, grocery provider and community partner, we have a responsibility to help keep our associates, customers and communities safe. according to the cdc, wearing a facial covering, combined with social distancing and frequent hand washing, has been scientifically proven to reduce the spread of covid-19. starting july 22, we will require all customers in all locations to wear a mask when shopping in our stores, joining our associates who continue to wear masks. we are taking this extra step now because we recognize additional precautions are needed to protect our country. "]}
